text:
PERCEIVED STRESS

Please read the statements below and for each select the response that best reflects your opinion. There are no right or wrong answers.

Key:
1=Strongly disagree
2=Disagree
3=Slightly disagree
4=Neither agree nor disagree
5=Slightly agree
6=Agree
7=Strongly agree
In the last month I have been upset because of something that happened unexpectedly.
In the last month, I have felt unable to control the important things in life.
In the last month, I have felt nervous and stressed.
In the last month, I have felt confident about my ability to handle personal problems.
In the last month, I have felt that things were going my way.
In the last month, I have found that I could not cope with all the things that I had to do.
In the last month, I have been able to control irritations in my life.
In the last month, I have felt that I was on top of things.
In the last month, I have been angered because of things that happened that were outside of my control.
In the last month, I have felt that difficulties were piling up so high that I could not overcome them.
